{"type":"message","id":"517eea10","parentId":"bc88dfad","timestamp":"2026-04-09T03:05:14.187Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_47d65583006e47b3bff097c1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/lvzheng/.openclaw/workspace-assistant-sdd-special/sdd-article.md","edits":[{"oldText":"### 1.1 远古时代（1960s—1980s）","newText":"### 1.1 早期年代（1960s—1980s）"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":65,"output":82,"cacheRead":20556,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20703,"cost":{"input":0.000078,"output":0.000328,"cacheRead":0.00493344,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00533944}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775703905484,"responseId":"20260409110507d51bc93e5e14410c"}}
{"type":"message","id":"b5940b51","parentId":"517eea10","timestamp":"2026-04-09T03:05:14.220Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_47d65583006e47b3bff097c1","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced 1 block(s) in /Users/lvzheng/.openclaw/workspace-assistant-sdd-special/sdd-article.md."}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n  21 SDD 不是某个人的发明，也不是某种方法论的品牌名。它是一条持续了六十年的思想脉络，每一次浪潮都在回答同一个问题：**如何让\"做什么\"比\"怎么做\"更清晰？**\n  22 \n  23 回顾这条脉络，可以看到一个清晰的趋势——SDD 从需要数学博士学位才能使用的\"贵族专用工具\"，一步步演变为任何开发者都能上手的日常实践。而 AI 编码的出现，则让这个过程完成了最后一步。\n  24 \n- 25 ### 1.1 远古时代（1960s—1980s）：用数学定义正确性\n+ 25 ### 1.1 早期年代（1960s—1980s）：用数学定义正确性\n  26 \n  27 软件危机催生了软件工程，也催生了最早的 SDD 实践——只不过那时它叫\"形式化规格\"（Formal Specification）。\n  28 \n  29 **Z Notation**（1970s）基于集合论，用数学符号精确描述系统的状态和操作 [1]。**VDM**（Vienna Development Method）由 IBM 维也纳实验室提出，是最早的系统化形式化方法之一 [2]。**TLA+**（Leslie Lamport）用数学逻辑描述并发系统的行为 [3]。**B-Method**（Jean-Raymond Abrial）更进一步，将形式化规格与逐步细化结合，能够在数学上证明实现是正确的 [4]。\n     ...","firstChangedLine":25},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775703914219}}
{"type":"message","id":"5e1d5280","parentId":"b5940b51","timestamp":"2026-04-09T03:05:16.893Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"改好了，`1.1 远古时代` → `1.1 早期年代`。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":116,"output":22,"cacheRead":20620,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20758,"cost":{"input":0.0001392,"output":0.000088,"cacheRead":0.0049488,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005176}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775703914221,"responseId":"20260409110515b7a6ca51999748cb"}}
{"type":"message","id":"d8c1db15","parentId":"5e1d5280","timestamp":"2026-04-09T03:07:58.197Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Thu 2026-04-09 11:07 GMT+8] 五、AI 编码时代，SDD 能走多远？这个标题感觉有点问题，从文章看，其实SDD从软件工程一开始就有了一直到现在，只是形式上的变化，“SDD 能走多远”，似乎是个伪命题"}],"timestamp":1775704078193}}
{"type":"message","id":"591937fb","parentId":"d8c1db15","timestamp":"2026-04-09T03:08:05.183Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"说得对。SDD 本身不是新事物，从 60 年代的形式化方法到现在的 spec-driven AI coding，核心思想一直都在。\"能走多远\"暗示它还在起步试探，但实际上它已经走了五六十年了。\n\n几个替代方向：\n\n**强调\"回归\"或\"重获新生\"：**\n- **五、AI 时代，SDD 的回归与新生**\n- **五、AI 编码时代，SDD 迎来最好的时刻**\n\n**强调\"进化\"或\"升级\"：**\n- **五、从形式化验证到 AI 编码：SDD 的六十年进化**\n- **五、AI 编码时代，SDD 的下一个形态**\n\n**更中性客观：**\n- **五、AI 编码时代下的 SDD**\n- **五、SDD 在 AI 编码时代的演进**\n\n你觉得哪个方向更对味？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":129,"output":184,"cacheRead":20735,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21048,"cost":{"input":0.0001548,"output":0.000736,"cacheRead":0.0049764,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0058671999999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775704078196,"responseId":"202604091108005f5acf2aeb084e48"}}
