{"type":"message","id":"4e3aaaa7","parentId":"1ef24a2c","timestamp":"2026-04-09T03:15:16.461Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_8688b075bbbe495eb4280ba6","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"AI generated code quality debate 2024 2025\",\n  \"provider\": \"duckduckgo\",\n  \"count\": 5,\n  \"tookMs\": 4503,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"duckduckgo\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"786443211b390420\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAI Copilot Code Quality: 2025 Data Suggests 4x Growth in Code Clones ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"786443211b390420\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.gitclear.com/ai_assistant_code_quality_2025_research\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"fd40f3f601d177b7\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nEmerging trends: 4x more code cloning, \\\"copy/paste\\\" exceeds \\\"moved\\\" code for first time in history. Includes 2025 projections. Stack Overflow's 2024 Developer Survey showed that 63% of professional developers are currently using AI in their development process, with another 14% saying they plan to begin using AI soon.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"fd40f3f601d177b7\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.gitclear.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"b67d83192b112547\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAssessing the Quality and Security of AI-Generated Code: A Quantitative ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"b67d83192b112547\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://arxiv.org/abs/2508.14727\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"3f6510f02eb37a81\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nThese results indicate that LLM- generated code requires verification in order to be considered production-ready. This study found no direct correlation between a model's functional performance (measured by Pass@1 rate of unit tests) and the overall quality and security of its generated code , measured by the number of SonarQube issues in ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"3f6510f02eb37a81\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"arxiv.org\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"5152688812ba377e\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nPDF I S S R J I\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"5152688812ba377e\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.issrj.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Evaluation-of-the-Code-Quality-Generated-by-Generative-AI.pdf\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"a23b159004ead20b\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAbstract: This study aims to evaluate and differentiate the effectiveness of the leading Generative- AI tools for code generation by examining key code quality metrics. The research focuses on the evaluation of correctness, readability, and the efficiency of GenAI code . The research methodology comprised two stages: an initial benchmark of four generative AI tools, followed by further ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"a23b159004ead20b\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.issrj.org\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"bde497c512e371e4\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nPDF The Impact Of AI-Generated Code On Software Quality And Developer ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"bde497c512e371e4\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.iosrjournals.org/iosr-jce/papers/Vol27-issue4/Ser-4/E2704043137.pdf\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"5bb44683fbb6796e\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAI-generated code introduces challenges that affect both the quality of software and the productivity of developers [2] [3]. The core problem lies in balancing the speed of code generation with the reliability and maintainability of the resulting code .\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"5bb44683fbb6796e\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.iosrjournals.org\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"5814161c2727b56a\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nPDF 2025 State of Al Code Quality - qodo.ai\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"5814161c2727b56a\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.qodo.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/2025-State-of-AI-Code-Quality.pdf\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"cad330580b9bd75d\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nConfidence feels good: how trusting Al- generated code builds happier engineers We asked developers how Al affects their job satisfaction-and found that confidence in the quality of the code matters just as much as the code itself.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"cad330580b9bd75d\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.qodo.ai\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"AI generated code quality debate 2024 2025","provider":"duckduckgo","count":5,"tookMs":4503,"externalContent":{"untrusted":true,"source":"web_search","provider":"duckduckgo","wrapped":true},"results":[{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"786443211b390420\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nAI Copilot Code Quality: 2025 Data Suggests 4x Growth in Code Clones ...\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"786443211b390420\">>>","url":"https://www.gitclear.com/ai_assistant_code_quality_2025_research","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"fd40f3f601d177b7\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nEmerging trends: 4x more code cloning, \"copy/paste\" exceeds \"moved\" code for first time in history. Includes 2025 projections. Stack Overflow's 2024 Developer Survey showed that 63% of professional developers are currently using AI in their development process, with another 14% saying they plan to begin using AI soon.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"fd40f3f601d177b7\">>>","siteName":"www.gitclear.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"b67d83192b112547\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nAssessing the Quality and Security of AI-Generated Code: A Quantitative ...\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"b67d83192b112547\">>>","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2508.14727","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"3f6510f02eb37a81\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nThese results indicate that LLM- generated code requires verification in order to be considered production-ready. This study found no direct correlation between a model's functional performance (measured by Pass@1 rate of unit tests) and the overall quality and security of its generated code , measured by the number of SonarQube issues in ...\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"3f6510f02eb37a81\">>>","siteName":"arxiv.org"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"5152688812ba377e\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nPDF I S S R J I\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"5152688812ba377e\">>>","url":"https://www.issrj.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Evaluation-of-the-Code-Quality-Generated-by-Generative-AI.pdf","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"a23b159004ead20b\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nAbstract: This study aims to evaluate and differentiate the effectiveness of the leading Generative- AI tools for code generation by examining key code quality metrics. The research focuses on the evaluation of correctness, readability, and the efficiency of GenAI code . The research methodology comprised two stages: an initial benchmark of four generative AI tools, followed by further ...\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"a23b159004ead20b\">>>","siteName":"www.issrj.org"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"bde497c512e371e4\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nPDF The Impact Of AI-Generated Code On Software Quality And Developer ...\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"bde497c512e371e4\">>>","url":"https://www.iosrjournals.org/iosr-jce/papers/Vol27-issue4/Ser-4/E2704043137.pdf","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"5bb44683fbb6796e\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nAI-generated code introduces challenges that affect both the quality of software and the productivity of developers [2] [3]. The core problem lies in balancing the speed of code generation with the reliability and maintainability of the resulting code .\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"5bb44683fbb6796e\">>>","siteName":"www.iosrjournals.org"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"5814161c2727b56a\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nPDF 2025 State of Al Code Quality - qodo.ai\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"5814161c2727b56a\">>>","url":"https://www.qodo.ai/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/2025-State-of-AI-Code-Quality.pdf","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"cad330580b9bd75d\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nConfidence feels good: how trusting Al- generated code builds happier engineers We asked developers how Al affects their job satisfaction-and found that confidence in the quality of the code matters just as much as the code itself.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"cad330580b9bd75d\">>>","siteName":"www.qodo.ai"}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775704516454}}
{"type":"message","id":"f7a87954","parentId":"4e3aaaa7","timestamp":"2026-04-09T03:15:16.465Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_3a607ada76754eb7a11de8ec","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"Kent Beck AI code quality verification bottleneck\",\n  \"provider\": \"duckduckgo\",\n  \"count\": 5,\n  \"tookMs\": 3512,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"duckduckgo\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"8ec0271b36e19755\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAI Code Verification Bottleneck: 96% Don't Trust Output\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"8ec0271b36e19755\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://byteiota.com/ai-code-verification-bottleneck-96-dont-trust-output-2/\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"081d778d64d35c49\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nThe verification bottleneck won't resolve itself. As AI code volume rises toward 65% of all commits, teams that build automated verification workflows will maintain code quality . Those that rely on manual review will drown in verification debt. The future isn't \\\" code faster with AI\\\"—it's \\\"verify at the speed of generation.\\\"\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"081d778d64d35c49\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"byteiota.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"5520c4bb6a3c6db4\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nThe Verification Bottleneck Is The New Software Engineering Crisis\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"5520c4bb6a3c6db4\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://medium.com/@the_atomic_architect/the-verification-bottleneck-is-the-new-software-engineering-crisis-b381eb2d74d6\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"1a175410f63c6537\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAI can generate code in seconds, but proving that polished code is safe, correct, and production-worthy is becoming the new crisis in software engineering.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"1a175410f63c6537\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"medium.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"8a7fd251051de8b8\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nCode Verification Emerges as AI's Next Bottleneck\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"8a7fd251051de8b8\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://themeridiem.com/ai-machine-learning/2026/03/30/code-verification-emerges-as-ai-s-next-bottleneck\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"4f7a1bb445a5a355\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nQodo's $70M raise signals the shift from AI code generation to quality assurance as the critical challenge in software development.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"4f7a1bb445a5a355\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"themeridiem.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"cf28d60e36efd63b\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nThe AI Verification Bottleneck: Developer Toil Isn't Shrinking\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"cf28d60e36efd63b\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://thenewstack.io/the-ai-verification-bottleneck-developer-toil-isnt-shrinking/\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"4dd144f86386ddec\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nThe current explosion in generation volume is moving at a breakneck pace, as developers predict that the share of AI -assisted code in their repositories, currently sitting at 42%, will surge to 65% by 2027 — an increase of over half in just two years. Sonar is the gold standard for integrated code quality and code security - for ALL code .\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"4dd144f86386ddec\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"thenewstack.io\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"e34b31fb9add56d2\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nThe Verification Bottleneck: Why Your AI Tools Are Making ... - LinkedIn\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"e34b31fb9add56d2\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.linkedin.com/pulse/verification-bottleneck-why-your-ai-tools-making-team-rob-foster-56o2c\",\n      \"snippet\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"3d37b093929f1ae5\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nFor every hour your team spends generating code with AI , how many hours are spent reviewing, testing, and integrating that output? If the ratio is climbing month over month, you have a bottleneck ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"3d37b093929f1ae5\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.linkedin.com\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"Kent Beck AI code quality verification bottleneck","provider":"duckduckgo","count":5,"tookMs":3512,"externalContent":{"untrusted":true,"source":"web_search","provider":"duckduckgo","wrapped":true},"results":[{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"8ec0271b36e19755\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nAI Code Verification Bottleneck: 96% Don't Trust Output\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"8ec0271b36e19755\">>>","url":"https://byteiota.com/ai-code-verification-bottleneck-96-dont-trust-output-2/","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"081d778d64d35c49\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nThe verification bottleneck won't resolve itself. As AI code volume rises toward 65% of all commits, teams that build automated verification workflows will maintain code quality . Those that rely on manual review will drown in verification debt. The future isn't \" code faster with AI\"—it's \"verify at the speed of generation.\"\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"081d778d64d35c49\">>>","siteName":"byteiota.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"5520c4bb6a3c6db4\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nThe Verification Bottleneck Is The New Software Engineering Crisis\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"5520c4bb6a3c6db4\">>>","url":"https://medium.com/@the_atomic_architect/the-verification-bottleneck-is-the-new-software-engineering-crisis-b381eb2d74d6","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"1a175410f63c6537\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nAI can generate code in seconds, but proving that polished code is safe, correct, and production-worthy is becoming the new crisis in software engineering.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"1a175410f63c6537\">>>","siteName":"medium.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"8a7fd251051de8b8\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nCode Verification Emerges as AI's Next Bottleneck\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"8a7fd251051de8b8\">>>","url":"https://themeridiem.com/ai-machine-learning/2026/03/30/code-verification-emerges-as-ai-s-next-bottleneck","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"4f7a1bb445a5a355\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nQodo's $70M raise signals the shift from AI code generation to quality assurance as the critical challenge in software development.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"4f7a1bb445a5a355\">>>","siteName":"themeridiem.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"cf28d60e36efd63b\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nThe AI Verification Bottleneck: Developer Toil Isn't Shrinking\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"cf28d60e36efd63b\">>>","url":"https://thenewstack.io/the-ai-verification-bottleneck-developer-toil-isnt-shrinking/","snippet":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"4dd144f86386ddec\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nThe current explosion in generation volume is moving at a breakneck pace, as developers predict that the share of AI -assisted code in their repositories, currently sitting at 42%, will surge to 65% by 2027 — an increase of over half in just two years. Sonar is the gold standard for integrated code quality and code security - for ALL code .\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"4dd144f86386ddec\">>>","siteName":"thenewstack.io"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONT