{"type":"message","id":"4f7edf7f","parentId":"43871e26","timestamp":"2026-04-09T06:08:35.029Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Thu 2026-04-09 14:08 GMT+8] 一、SDD 的发展脉络，这部分把形式化规格、TDD、BDD、接口即契约都归于SDD的发展，你觉得逻辑上有问题吗，是不是把规格过于泛化了？"}],"timestamp":1775714915026}}
