{"type":"message","id":"a5cda8cf","parentId":"b72fc6d9","timestamp":"2026-04-09T07:05:51.019Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"改好了。两处调整：\n\n1. `SDD` → `\"设计先行\"`，主语对齐\n2. `做不起` → `成本太高，难以持续`，表述更准确"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":205,"output":43,"cacheRead":38742,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38990,"cost":{"input":0.00024599999999999996,"output":0.00017199999999999998,"cacheRead":0.009298079999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.009716079999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775718344515,"responseId":"2026040915054924d6d22c6a684360"}}
{"type":"message","id":"ecde80a4","parentId":"a5cda8cf","timestamp":"2026-04-09T07:09:37.867Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Thu 2026-04-09 15:09 GMT+8] 其实，你会发现，因为设计先行成本很高，所以早起的瀑布模型开发方式很难被执行，然后敏捷开发大行其道。当然敏捷开发并不是说不做设计，而是弱化、裁剪了不必要的设计，本质上还是成本问题。"}],"timestamp":1775718577863}}
{"type":"message","id":"f04d37d4","parentId":"ecde80a4","timestamp":"2026-04-09T07:09:48.650Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"这个洞察很好。把\"设计先行\"的困境和瀑布模型→敏捷开发的演进连起来，逻辑链条就完整了：\n\n> 设计先行成本高 → 瀑布模型严格执行但难以落地 → 敏捷开发用\"够用就好\"替代\"一步到位\" → 本质上不是否定设计先行，而是对成本问题的务实回应\n\n这段话适合放在第一章的开篇或 1.2 小节之前，作为从形式化方法到 TDD/BDD 的过渡桥梁——解释了为什么\"设计先行\"需要不断寻找更轻量的形式。\n\n不过要注意一点：这个因果链里说的是**传统的重度设计先行**（比如瀑布模型里 upfront design），而不是\"设计先行\"这个理念本身。敏捷并没有抛弃设计先行，只是换了方式——比如 Scrum 的 Sprint Planning、User Story、Definition of Done，本质上都是轻量级的设计定义。\n\n要我把这段内容补进文章里吗？放在哪个位置你觉得合适？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":150,"output":200,"cacheRead":38946,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39296,"cost":{"input":0.00017999999999999998,"output":0.0007999999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00934704,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01032704}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775718577866,"responseId":"20260409150940ebae0e3209f34b9a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"84631f43","parentId":"f04d37d4","timestamp":"2026-04-09T07:11:43.132Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Thu 2026-04-09 15:11 GMT+8] 不用加了，改的很好，避免了SDD的泛化，又把文章提高了一个层面，从更高的工程视角切入到SDD"}],"timestamp":1775718703128}}
{"type":"message","id":"c4da62da","parentId":"84631f43","timestamp":"2026-04-09T07:11:51.760Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"确实，\"设计先行\"这个框架让整篇文章的格局不一样了——SDD 不再是孤立的某个方法论，而是软件工程六十年来的一条持久主线上的最新节点。读者读完第一章会自然理解：SDD 不是凭空冒出来的，也不是什么新概念，它是\"先定义、再实现\"这个朴素思想在 AI 时代终于找到了可落地的形式。\n\n继续往下看还有要调整的地方吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":285,"output":90,"cacheRead":39095,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39470,"cost":{"input":0.00034199999999999996,"output":0.00035999999999999997,"cacheRead":0.009382799999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.010084799999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775718703131,"responseId":"20260409151148c4aefcf315ed4c17"}}
{"type":"message","id":"f4ebe2ba","parentId":"c4da62da","timestamp":"2026-04-09T07:48:19.518Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Thu 2026-04-09 15:48 GMT+8] 所以这从一个侧面也体现出，OpenClaw的记忆做的有多么粗糙，你都不知道你之前做的什么"}],"timestamp":1775720899513}}
